rs to have accepted the example as a reasonable illustration of the rule despite the technical inaccuracy — the output JSON is identical to the pre-fix version, indicating the agent either did not flag it as requiring correction or produced no change."}]}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":26892,"cache_read_input_tokens":29902,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":26892,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"42301d65-72ee-4301-afa9-5af76d762cc5","uuid":"3271a400-9150-4645-a97e-9f1d2e446f05"}
